# id: StringTermsIT -> public void testDontCacheScripts() throws Exception
commentText: Make sure that a request using a script does not get cached and a request_not using a script does get cached.
codeText: public void testDontCacheScripts() throws Exception {_        assertAcked(prepareCreate("cache_test_idx").addMapping("type", "d", "type=keyword")_                .setSettings(Settings.builder().put("requests.cache.enable", true).put("number_of_shards", 1).put("number_of_replicas", 1))_                .get())__        indexRandom(true, client().prepareIndex("cache_test_idx", "type", "1").setSource("s", "foo"),_                client().prepareIndex("cache_test_idx", "type", "2").setSource("s", "bar"))___        _        assertThat(client().admin().indices().prepareStats("cache_test_idx").setRequestCache(true).get().getTotal().getRequestCache()_                .getHitCount(), equalTo(0L))__        assertThat(client().admin().indices().prepareStats("cache_test_idx").setRequestCache(true).get().getTotal().getRequestCache()_                .getMissCount(), equalTo(0L))___        _        SearchResponse r = client().prepareSearch("cache_test_idx").setSize(0)_                .addAggregation(_                        terms("terms").field("d").script(_                            new Script(ScriptType.INLINE, CustomScriptPlugin.NAME, "'foo_' + _value", Collections.emptyMap())))_                .get()__        assertSearchResponse(r)___        assertThat(client().admin().indices().prepareStats("cache_test_idx").setRequestCache(true).get().getTotal().getRequestCache()_                .getHitCount(), equalTo(0L))__        assertThat(client().admin().indices().prepareStats("cache_test_idx").setRequestCache(true).get().getTotal().getRequestCache()_                .getMissCount(), equalTo(0L))___        _        _        r = client().prepareSearch("cache_test_idx").setSize(0).addAggregation(terms("terms").field("d")).get()__        assertSearchResponse(r)___        assertThat(client().admin().indices().prepareStats("cache_test_idx").setRequestCache(true).get().getTotal().getRequestCache()_                .getHitCount(), equalTo(0L))__        assertThat(client().admin().indices().prepareStats("cache_test_idx").setRequestCache(true).get().getTotal().getRequestCache()_                .getMissCount(), equalTo(1L))__    }
